for a connection. a reason.

286
00:16:24.275 --> 00:16:26.611
Will there ever be
a good enough reason?

287
00:16:31.658 --> 00:16:33.702
We haven't heard from
Johnny in a couple of days.

288
00:16:33.785 --> 00:16:35.162
We went to his apartment.

289
00:16:35.245 --> 00:16:37.456
His TV was missing.
car. everything else.

290
00:16:37.539 --> 00:16:40.250
Every stitch of clothing
was there.

291
