long enough.

298
00:17:06.234 --> 00:17:08.111
And Rob was how old?

299
00:17:09.362 --> 00:17:12.658
-Fifteen.
-Johnny was 19. an adult.

300
00:17:12.741 --> 00:17:13.784
-I didn't mean any...
