Look. I never had no lobster.
Randy.

319
00:18:17.681 --> 00:18:21.184
I'm just saying. crayfish
are like little lobsters

320
00:18:21.267 --> 00:18:23.437
and lobsters
are like giant ocean bugs.

321
00:18:25.855 --> 00:18:27.441
Man. that's weird.

322
00:18:27.524 --> 00:18:29.192
Good with butter.

323
00:18:30.527 --> 00:18:31.695
Good with butter?

324
00:18:31.778 --> 00:18:33.196
You're saying giant ocean bugs

325
00:18:33.279 --> 00:18:34.489
-are good with butter?
-Shut the fuck up. Randy.

326
00:18:34.572 --> 00:18:35.616
Yes. they are.

327
00:18:35.699 --> 00:18:36.867
That's what I've heard.

328
00:18:36.950 --> 00:18:38.577
-What the fuck?
-How about you try them first

329
00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:39.911
and then you could say that?

330
00:18:40.995 --> 00:18:42.872
Always judging.

331
00:18:44.791 --> 00:18:46.168
You miss it?

332
00:18:46.251 --> 00:18:47.544
Kentucky?

333
