338
00:19:05.395 --> 00:19:08.273
-Stop. stop! Calm down!
-Jesus.

339
00:19:08.356 --> 00:19:10.317
I mean. skip it. Shit.

340
00:19:10.400 --> 00:19:12.610
Maybe you. not me.

341
