357
00:20:05.663 --> 00:20:07.457
We're gonna need
a real nuts-and-bolts guy

358
00:20:07.540 --> 00:20:10.627
to keep shovelin' off the shit
Kunkle throws our way.

359
00:20:10.710 --> 00:20:12.504
We're talking
thousands of dollars

360
00:20:12.587 --> 00:20:14.423
