as your judge. jury.
and executioner. remember that?

379
00:21:04.556 --> 00:21:06.558
Remember that?
-Yeah.

380
00:21:07.892 --> 00:21:10.312
But there is one thing I can do.

381
00:21:10.395 --> 00:21:12.522
