442
00:25:17.600 --> 00:25:18.977
Ain't stoppin' those cops.

443
00:25:19.060 --> 00:25:20.604
Yeah. Well.
sittin' doin' nothin'

444
00:25:20.687 --> 00:25:22.105
and dyin' ain't no choice.

445
00:25:22.188 --> 00:25:23.606
It's all we got.

446
00:25:24.983 --> 00:25:26.109
Proud of you.

447
00:25:29.696 --> 00:25:30.739
Why?

448
00:25:31.114 --> 00:25:33.533
Am I that much of a monster?

449
00:25:33.616 --> 00:25:35.869
I yell at you
when you deserve it.

450
00:25:36.453 --> 00:25:38.621
Tell you do right
when you do right.

451
00:25:38.955 --> 00:25:40.999
That pizza job you got is right.

452
00:25:41.082 --> 00:25:42.501
I can't do it
the rest of my life.

453
00:25:42.584 --> 00:25:43.877
Ah. rest of your life.

454
00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:47.422
You're 13. It's a start.

455
00:25:47.505 --> 00:25:50.842
Let's go.
Bus will be here soon.

456
