467
00:26:25.043 --> 00:26:27.671
Ain't going nowhere. you shoddy.

468
00:26:27.754 --> 00:26:29.589
You fuckin' Hillbilly.

469
00:26:30.382 --> 00:26:32.258
You talkin'
to the Harrison Gents?

470
00:26:33.843 --> 00:26:35.554
