478
00:26:49.150 --> 00:26:50.569
I'm not joinin' shit.

479
00:26:50.652 --> 00:26:52.529
They don't take no nicely.

480
00:26:53.029 --> 00:26:54.531
Fuck 'em.

481
00:26:54.614 --> 00:26:58.243
Yeah. Be peelin' you
off the sidewalk.

482
00:26:59.744 --> 00:27:00.995
I gotta go.

483
