485
00:27:06.042 --> 00:27:07.502
I'm workin' a double.

486
00:27:07.585 --> 00:27:09.546
I'll make sure ma
let's you stay the night.

487
00:27:09.629 --> 00:27:10.880
Of course.

488
00:27:11.089 --> 00:27:12.716
Say bye.

489
00:27:19.973 --> 00:27:23.268
Your Honor. my client
