507
00:28:15.779 --> 00:28:17.322
But step back a moment.

508
00:28:17.405 --> 00:28:19.324
What does this image tell you?

509
00:28:19.949 --> 00:28:22.327
It tells you
that the Secret Service

510
00:28:22.410 --> 00:28:24.705
did not consider John a danger.

511
00:28:24.788 --> 00:28:26.915
Your Honor. the Secret Service's

512
00:28:26.998 --> 00:28:29.710
