519
00:28:45.266 --> 00:28:47.394
Invited them into his home.
cooked them dinner.

520
00:28:47.477 --> 00:28:49.062
I mean. come on.

521
00:28:49.521 --> 00:28:52.149
John Gacy
is a pillar of this community.

522
00:28:52.232 --> 00:28:55.027
And as such. should be
treated with the respect

523
